Package: whisper-input
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.12), xdotool, xclip, pulseaudio-utils, libportaudio2, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, libgirepository-2.0-dev, gcc, libcairo2-dev, pkg-config
Recommends: libcudart12
Maintainer: Jing <pkulijing@gmail.com>
Description: Linux voice input tool
 Press and hold a hotkey to speak, release to transcribe and type
 the result into the focused window. Uses local SenseVoice model
 for Chinese/English speech recognition.
 .
 Features:
  - Local speech recognition (no internet required)
  - Chinese/English mixed input
  - Configurable hotkey and settings via browser UI
  - System tray integration
  - XDG autostart support
